---
description: Global rules for Market Pulse Radar
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Python 3.11 + uv. Run tools via `uv run ...`.
- Type hints everywhere; mypy --strict clean. Format with ruff+black.
- Keep functions small & pure; config-driven (no magic numbers).
- Layers: collectors → pipelines → repos/db → api. No cross-layer imports.
- All datetimes tz-aware in UTC.
- Use DTOs at boundaries (models/dto.py).
- Prefer sync SQLAlchemy 2 + psycopg; don’t mix async unless we switch.
- No secrets in repo; use .env locally and CI secrets.
